page.title: 06 Unwillingly To School
page.content: I was late for school this morning because I went to sleep at 11:30 last night. At 8:10 this morning my little brother woke me up and by the time I got dressed it was 8:20. I had a quarter of an hour to find my trainers. I took twenty minutes to have my breakfast and it took me five minutes to make my bed. By the time I changed my shirt it was 8:59 and one of my legs was asleep so I could not run to school. When I found a coat peg the time was 9:10. I have a varoucca on my foot so it was hard to walk to school. On the way to school there was a road digger in Foundry Lane so I had to take the long route to school.
